    "Finally, Sect. 5.2.3 describes the full set of 21 SLR tools according to the general features.",
    "As reported in Table 1, 19 tools use AI for the screening phase.",
    "In the following, we analyse them according to the 11 AI features.",
    "To eliminate repetitions, this discussion combines the features input and text representation into the category Input Data and Text Representation.",
    "Moreover, the output feature is discussed within the context of the SLR Task, as it is contingent upon the specific task requirements."
